race.comment: Big field and plenty of pressure. TOO MANY THOUGHTS (2) is going great and looks the one to beat with any luck from the draw. Winner here two back before losing in a bob last time. Races handy and with even luck will go close. LAVONI (10) doesn't win out of turn but does looks well placed here. Dropped back to 1100m last time and was solid but this extra trip is more suitable and will be tough to hold out. NUTS 'N' BOLTS (1) was out at Moree last time and was beaten a head over 1200m. Freshened and has trialled since. Looks tough to hold out. BLUE CHIP GIRL (3) is better than the latest but freshened and on good record here will be charging late. ALFA LILY (15) is working up to a win. Has good early speed and is among the top chances.
